additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: IRRITANT. AVOID CONTACT WITH EYES AND SKIN. DO NOT SWALLOW. WASH HANDS AFTER USE. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. In case of contact with eyes, rinse immediately with plenty of water. If swallowed, do NOT induce vomiting. Give two glasses of water. For advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone Australia 131 126, New Zealand 0800764 766) or a doctor and show this label. Some items are unsuitable for machine dishwashing: all aluminium ware, leaded crystal and glass, decorated glassware, old or hand painted china, wooden or bone-handled items.
